)

Populate a pose service object with the wanted robotic manipulator pose.

Parameters
relativeTrue if the position is relative to current pose. False if the position is absolute in relation to the world reference frame.
positionInclude position in the pose. If false, the manipulator will only reorient.
xDesired position in X direction.
yDesired position in Y direction.
zDesired position in Z direction.
orientationInclude orientation in the pose. If false, the manipulator will only reposition.
rollDesired roll angle.
pitchDesired pitch angle.
yawDesired yaw angle.
